  "body": "This causes StartMessenger to fail (as described in https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/8552), due to the TorrentConfig port being already used.\r\n\r\nSome possible solutions are:\r\n- Create a variable similar to WAKUV2_PORT should be added to allow setting up the torrent config port. \r\n- Replace WAKUV2_PORT by a PORT_SHIFT variable that receives an integer. Then, everywhere we use a port number, we add an int(PORT_SHIFT), i.e:\r\n  - Instance 1, run without variable:\r\n    - wakuv2 port: 60000\r\n    - udp port: 9000\r\n    - torrent_config port: 9025\r\n  - Instance 2, run with PORT_SHIFT=2\r\n    - wakuv2 port: 60000 + 2\r\n    - udp port: 9000 + 2\r\n    - torrent_config port: 9025 + 2",
